&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support the development of positioning and messaging for VIP&#39;s product portfolio, including AI-driven features, supplier tools, and distributor solutions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create sales enablement content — battlecards, objection handling, feature one-pagers that help reps win competitive deals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Execute product launch plans in partnership with the Senior Product Marketer, demand gen, and product teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct win/loss analysis and customer interviews to surface insights that sharpen messaging and improve conversion&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain VIP&#39;s competitive intelligence library — tracking competitor moves, pricing changes, and market positioning&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support the development of case studies, testimonials, and ROI calculators that help buyers justify purchase decisions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with demand gen to develop campaign messaging for product-led campaigns&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work with the design team to direct web page design and web copy that is designed to convert visitors to the demand gen funnel.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Write customer newsletters, blogs, white papers, and other lead-gen content as&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
