&lt;p&gt;Are you the person who can turn a cardboard box into a spaceship? Do you believe that “why?” is the most exciting question in the world? If you’ve got patience for days and a laugh that’s contagious, we want to meet you!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;VIP’s Roots Early Education Center&lt;/strong&gt; is looking for passionate, energetic, and nurturing Child Care Teachers to join our team and make a real difference in the lives of our littlest explorers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why You&#39;ll Love It Here&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Best Coworkers&lt;/strong&gt;: They’re all under four feet tall, incredibly creative, and always happy to see you 😂&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Growth Opportunities&lt;/strong&gt;: We value your expertise and provide the tools and environment for you to refine your craft and take your career in early childhood education to the next level&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Play with a Purpose:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;Your “office” is a world of art, stories, and outdoor adventures.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You&#39;ll Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create a safe “home away from home” environment where kiddos can build their social skills, practical capabilities and self-esteem&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lend hands-on activities that spark curiosity&amp;nbsp;and encourage children&#39;s learning and development (think: finger painting, music, and science experiments)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be a hero to parents by providing peace of mind and daily updates&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Navigate the highs (first words) and the lows (spilled milk) with grace and a smile&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Are You The One?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We aren’t just looking for a resume; we’re looking for a vibe. You’re a great fit if:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have a genuine love for early childhood education&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You’re a master at multitasking (and snack-dispensing)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You’re dependable, kind, and ready to get a little messy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You’re CPR Certified, background check-ready, enjoy professional development and love to work in a positive team environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Compensation:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;$23.00 - $25.00/hour&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Compensation is based on a variety of factors including skills, experience and industry background. The range listed here represents our best faith estimate for the role.&lt;/p&gt;
