&lt;p&gt;Vermont Information Processing (VIP) is looking for a detail-driven, customer-focused &lt;strong&gt;Sales Support Specialist&lt;/strong&gt; to join our Sales team. In this role, you’ll be the operational backbone of our sales function—keeping deals moving, data accurate, and customers informed. If you thrive in a fast-paced environment and love bringing order to complexity, we want to hear from you.&lt;/p&gt;
