&lt;p&gt;VIP is seeking a &lt;strong&gt;Senior&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;strong&gt;Data Architect&lt;/strong&gt; with expertise in dimensional modeling to design, implement, and optimize our enterprise data warehouse and analytics solutions. This role is instrumental in helping beverage distributors, suppliers, and retailers make data-driven decisions through scalable and high-performance data architectures. We are looking for a motivated self-starter who enjoys collaboration and innovation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Position Type:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;Full Time,&amp;nbsp;Hybrid - will be required to report to our office in Colchester, VT.&lt;/p&gt;
