&lt;li&gt;BS / MS in Computer Science or related field&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Minimum of 5 years experience in information technology with increasing responsibility in understanding and designing complex and enhancing existing relational database systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven track record of successfully managing all stages of large-scale database projects.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong understanding of Kimball-style dimensional modeling, including fact and dimension table design, slowly changing dimensions (SCDs), star and snowflake schemas, and best practices for optimizing ETL processes in a data warehouse environment&lt;/li&gt;
