&lt;li&gt;Excellent verbal and written communication skills to collaborate with technical and non-technical stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to explain complicated concepts in simple terms&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent attention to detail&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with database management software&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of SQL Server, Snowflake and DB2 is a plus!&lt;/li&gt;
